title: The Port Workspaces

creator: OfficeR&D
descriptionHtml: The Port Workspaces is a coworking space based in Oakland CA. Connect with community, book meeting rooms, and pay your bill all in one place.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
The Port Workspaces’s latest release comes with the following improvements:
- Members can now utilize the slick native flows of our app to access all bookable resources besides meeting rooms that are available on the web portal
- Members will now receive push notifications for any new activity on the open tickets/issues that they’ve submitted
- Numerous bug fixes
